{"tid":2081801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重PO  聽日!!!6.28 反國靜默遊行!!","createTime":"2020-06-27T13:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T03:33:35.000Z","uid":282534,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a64a413f4c476eab47d3b59c337c8edd89c1f556","tid":2081801,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kkhp36s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKkhp36s.jpg&h=9e49432c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#28Jun #佐敦 #靜默遊行 #SUCK活動<br />\n【6.28反國靜默遊行】<br />\n日期 : 6月28日 (日)<br />\n時間 : 15:00 - 17:00<br />\n路線 : 由佐敦A,B出口沿彌敦道行人道直到旺角解散<br />\n內容如下 : <br />\n1⃣15:00準時出發<br />\n2⃣不集合❗️不口號❗️不逗留❗️<br />\n3⃣彩虹衣著<br />\n4⃣請使用行人道進行本次行動<br />\n5⃣完成路程後請原地airdrop7.1有關文宣及離開<br />\n❗️如被狗隻打斷或任何突發行動請轉入內街沿內街自行繼續/解散<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou/19277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou%2F19277&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=6610d1ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou/19277</a> / <a href=\"https://lih.kg/fBLrkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fBLrkT</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7.1 文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzjG6j5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyzjG6j5.jpg&h=cdb7ce26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQpctyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQpctyr.jpg&h=a854d9bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKPjSZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKPjSZ7.jpg&h=61e49978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeBm6j8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeBm6j8.jpg&h=f38c7f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duRaZE9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FduRaZE9.jpg&h=86bfee89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連儂巴士計劃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVRFCrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVRFCrx.jpg&h=fe59ff40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubReGTh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubReGTh.jpg&h=f4c84fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便推廣 連儂巴士計劃<br />\n<br />\n只須要一支筆就可以係巴士上做有效既文宣<br />\n<br />\n其實要將巴士連儂化好簡單  <br />\n一支筆就夠  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但7.1係屬於香港人既 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.1一定要出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 19999 <br />\n<br />\n時間關係 <br />\n今次只你直接copy tg channel 上既野<br />\n<br />\n求原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686a8a87d40d6ba21d46f68814450fe098cb66a0","tid":2081801,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d80b071b95f36f7c29a5c1414797046538206ea","tid":2081801,"uid":120347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d01b6af5c1ec135965acd349c93d910d79e1b35","tid":2081801,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"聽日唔去，但起碼都去71！！！"},{"pid":"981b3926946b10d7d6a5e0a33dbaed95032d2d70","tid":2081801,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"泛民聽日記得貼好啲文宣<br />\n71大家都精神啲"},{"pid":"2dffe8da4106c59acf28bd053bc32ad3a2347acd","tid":2081801,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/